Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,----OP
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.94,0:02:03.43,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}誰かを悲しませてまで　笑えなくても
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.44,0:02:07.15,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}そう言って彼女は　うつむいてたんだ
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.16,0:02:13.88,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}夜に泣いた
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.66,0:02:21.66,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}冷たく張り付いて凍えている
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.90,0:02:28.83,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}降り続く現実に傘などない
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.43,0:02:35.40,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}生きていく事が戦いなんて
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.41,0:02:39.00,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}そんな理由だけで閉じ込められた
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.01,0:02:41.97,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}マイハートマイストーリー
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.09,0:02:49.54,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}泪のムコウが見えるの　輝いている
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.60,0:02:56.23,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}ちいさな窓には　あの頃みたいに　青い空がうつる
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.45,0:03:02.30,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}ああ鳥のように飛べはしないけど
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.06,0:03:14.47,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}誰かを悲しませたとき感じる痛み
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.51,0:03:21.76,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}忘れないように　そっと目を閉じて　泣いた
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.94,0:02:03.43,OPcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}若能让你忘却伤痛 我宁愿舍弃笑容
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.44,0:02:07.15,OPcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}如是言语的她 默然低下了头
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.16,0:02:13.88,OPcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}任凭泪水洗刷着夜色
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.66,0:02:21.66,OPcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}冷漠蔓延着冻结一切
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.90,0:02:28.83,OPcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}仿佛这无可喘息的现实
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.43,0:02:35.40,OPcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}生存就是战斗
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.41,0:02:39.00,OPcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}被这可悲的理由束缚着
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.01,0:02:41.97,OPcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}My heart my story
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.09,0:02:49.54,OPcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}泪水的彼岸 那闪耀的光芒
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.60,0:02:56.23,OPcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}狭小的窗口中 满眼是往昔的蓝天
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.45,0:03:02.30,OPcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}虽然无法像鸟儿一样飞翔
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.06,0:03:14.47,OPcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}为让悲伤永远铭记于心而生的痛苦
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.51,0:03:21.76,OPcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}为了忘却而闭目哭泣
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,----ED
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.79,0:20:50.29,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3\fad(200,200)}花は風に揺れ踊るように　雨は大地を潤すように
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.29,0:20:54.66,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3\fad(200,200)}この世界は寄り添い合い　生きてるのに
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.77,0:21:06.16,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3\fad(200,200)}なぜ人は傷付け合うの　なぜ別れは訪れるの
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.41,0:21:11.86,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3\fad(200,200)}君が遠くに行ってもまだ　いつもこの心の真ん中
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.91,0:21:16.18,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3\fad(200,200)}あの優しい笑顔で埋め尽くされたまま
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.33,0:21:25.34,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3\fad(200,200)}抱きしめた君の欠片に　痛み感じてもまだ
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.34,0:21:29.12,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3\fad(200,200)}繋がるから　信じてるよ　また逢えると
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.12,0:21:31.16,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3\fad(200,200)}I am waiting for your love
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.16,0:21:36.43,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3\fad(200,200)}I love you　I trust you
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.53,0:21:41.83,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3\fad(200,200)}君の孤独を分けて欲しい
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.96,0:21:47.13,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3\fad(200,200)}I love you　I trust you
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.31,0:21:52.70,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3\fad(200,200)}光でも闇でも
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.76,0:21:59.79,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3\fad(200,200)}二人だから信じ合える
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.92,0:22:05.21,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3\fad(200,200)}NO 離さないで
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.79,0:20:50.29,EDcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3\fad(200,200)}如同花朵随风起舞 如同雨水滋润大地
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.29,0:20:54.66,EDcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3\fad(200,200)}这个世界如此紧密不分 如此活泼生机
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.77,0:21:06.16,EDcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3\fad(200,200)}却为何人们要互相伤害 为何离别会突然降临
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.41,0:21:11.86,EDcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3\fad(200,200)}即便去往遥远的地方 你总是会活在我心底
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.91,0:21:16.18,EDcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3\fad(200,200)}那份温柔的笑颜依旧映在眼里
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.33,0:21:25.34,EDcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3\fad(200,200)}拥抱着你的碎片 刺痛着我的身体
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.34,0:21:29.12,EDcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3\fad(200,200)}但心心相连 因为我坚信 会再见到你
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.12,0:21:31.16,EDcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3\fad(200,200)}I am waiting for your love
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.16,0:21:36.43,EDcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3\fad(200,200)}I love you  I trust you
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.53,0:21:41.83,EDcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3\fad(200,200)}多么想分担你的孤寂
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.96,0:21:47.13,EDcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3\fad(200,200)}I love you  I trust you
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.31,0:21:52.70,EDcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3\fad(200,200)}无论身处黑暗或是光明
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.76,0:21:59.79,EDcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3\fad(200,200)}只要在一起就可以相信
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.92,0:22:05.21,EDcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3\fad(200,200)}永远不再分离
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,----Dialogue
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.60,0:00:10.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就没有别的办法了吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.14,0:00:11.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没有
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.67,0:00:15.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个时候…她…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.71,0:00:20.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已经不是艾纽·里特纳了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.15,0:00:22.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么说得这么肯定?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.48,0:00:24.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么呢…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.49,0:00:27.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过 我可以确定的是…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.45,0:00:31.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不那么做的话 莱尔·狄兰迪就会死
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.75,0:00:32.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么会…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.63,0:00:37.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,露易丝·哈勒维也是
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.64,0:00:40.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她被什么东西占据了而不能自拔
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.25,0:00:43.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有这种感觉
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.17,0:00:47.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你最近有些地方不对劲啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.03,0:00:49.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和一直以来不同
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.35,0:00:53.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为了检查舰内系统 将暂时切断电源
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.41,0:01:02.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,检查完毕
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.74,0:01:04.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,恢复一般供电
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.95,0:01:07.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,船控系统 恢复
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.76,0:01:09.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一切正常
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.35,0:01:12.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,米蕾娜 敌舰如何?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.63,0:01:14.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看样子已经不在可视范围内了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.91,0:01:15.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要放松
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.69,0:01:19.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也许会像之前一样中阴招	
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.60,0:01:20.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,提艾利亚
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.50,0:01:25.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,斯米拉琪小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.73,0:01:29.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在系统当机时 好像接到了紧急暗号通信
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.44,0:01:30.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,内容是?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.72,0:01:32.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只写了宙域坐标
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.71,0:01:36.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,地点是拉格朗日5
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.75,0:01:40.36,Notes,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}拉格朗日5 Eclipse
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.39,0:01:40.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,建设中断的殖民地 Eclipse
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.57,0:01:49.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.18,0:01:50.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我没事
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.83,0:01:54.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我还不能…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.31,0:03:33.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去拉格朗日5?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.77,0:03:38.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要回应那个发送坐标的人吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.39,0:03:39.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我很在意啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.75,0:03:41.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且 刹那也坚持要去
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.43,0:03:43.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,刹那他?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.79,0:03:46.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也赞成
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.97,0:03:47.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,伊恩
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.35,0:03:49.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拉格朗日5那里
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.72,0:03:52.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,避难的琳达他们也在继续着研究
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.91,0:03:55.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,顺利的话 也可以拿到计划中的新装备
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.59,0:03:59.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到达那里的话 还能进行Gundam的维修
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.12,0:04:02.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.78,0:04:05.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让我来掌舵?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.99,0:04:07.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拉塞受伤了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.32,0:04:10.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,必须找人来保护托勒密
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.55,0:04:13.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,打算不让我上战场吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.60,0:04:15.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和斯米卢诺夫大佐这么约定的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.34,0:04:18.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜托了 听我一次吧…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.11,0:04:19.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不听!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.06,0:04:20.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,索玛·皮瑞斯
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.83,0:04:23.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样的战斗持续下去的话 总有一天你…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.35,0:04:33.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,托勒密会迂回前进 引开敌人
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.35,0:04:35.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,趁这个机会 去和通信者接触
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.88,0:04:36.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.60,0:04:38.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.61,0:04:39.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是去帮助人吧?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.98,0:04:41.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是这样的话 我会协助的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.14,0:04:53.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,莱尔…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.08,0:04:58.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,之前的事 抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.41,0:05:01.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,过于感情用事了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.37,0:05:03.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不配做机师
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.88,0:05:04.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,莱尔 我…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.85,0:05:05.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,战斗吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.67,0:05:08.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我会战斗的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.94,0:05:12.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.38,0:05:19.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.39,0:05:22.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,灭了那帮变革者
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.13,0:05:26.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是为了KATARON 也不是为了天行者
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.93,0:05:29.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要以我自己的意志和他们战斗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.25,0:05:30.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.91,0:05:57.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哥哥…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.74,0:06:01.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,托勒密第一第三舱门打开
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.72,0:06:05.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,发射时机交予00
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.83,0:06:06.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,了解
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.99,0:06:09.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,00 刹那·F·塞艾 出发
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.85,0:06:12.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,0 Raiser 沙慈·库洛斯洛特 出发
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.95,0:06:17.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,0 Raiser DOCKING-MODE
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.61,0:06:28.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,00 Raiser 飞往拉格朗日5
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.76,0:06:37.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,光学摄像机捕捉到天行者的宇宙船
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.45,0:06:39.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,路线变更了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.20,0:06:41.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,继续追击
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.67,0:06:42.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明白
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.39,0:06:44.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}第三舰队 航向改变
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.20,0:06:47.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,击败天行者的话 反对势力的气势也会下降
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.27,0:06:52.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已经不能再信任那些自我主义的家伙了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.45,0:06:54.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为了回应片桐司令的期待
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.13,0:06:58.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要用压倒性的战力歼灭他们
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.53,0:07:00.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是怎么了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.33,0:07:02.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,连艾纽也被打败了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.19,0:07:04.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们可是变革者啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.25,0:07:07.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,00 Gundam…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.48,0:07:13.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拿下你了 00
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.83,0:07:18.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.05,0:07:30.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Gundam
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.07,0:07:44.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那种战斗方式… 不仅仅是依靠MS的性能…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.97,0:07:49.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,00的驾驶员开始革新了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.26,0:07:51.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哈? 你在说什么…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.51,0:07:53.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是这样话解释不了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.83,0:07:55.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你想说他是纯种
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.70,0:07:58.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,刹那·F·塞艾…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.16,0:08:02.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他会成为人类最初的变革者吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.55,0:08:05.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Gundam
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.63,0:08:08.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在这里啊 准尉
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.25,0:08:10.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,新型MA的维修…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.91,0:08:11.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,闭嘴
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.92,0:08:14.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别管我
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.74,0:08:17.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,准尉 怎么了?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.35,0:08:19.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我说了别…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.43,0:08:21.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,打扰你们了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.52,0:08:24.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Mr.武士道
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.81,0:08:25.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么事
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.25,0:08:28.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我和准尉的特别命令下达了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.84,0:08:29.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,准备出击
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.37,0:08:30.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.37,0:08:36.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请让我同行
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.46,0:08:39.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我会去征得古德曼准将的同意
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.48,0:08:41.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,随你
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.50,0:08:46.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你觉得能跟上我和准尉的机体吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.32,0:08:50.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,距到达目标还要花几天
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.57,0:08:52.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,休息一下吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.28,0:08:54.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就按你说的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.32,0:09:00.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你最近有些地方不对劲啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.00,0:09:06.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,刹那 你要改变 代替不能改变的我…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.40,0:09:08.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.28,0:09:11.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我 变了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.73,0:09:14.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在那终点有着什么东西
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.95,0:09:32.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诗琳吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.97,0:09:35.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,克劳斯 没事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.93,0:09:37.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,擦伤而已
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.55,0:09:40.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你也没事真是太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.19,0:09:43.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到宇宙去?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.89,0:09:46.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我和联邦军政变派残党接触了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.73,0:09:52.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在支部几乎全灭 再留在地上太危险了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.94,0:09:56.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 宇宙中KATARON的战力
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.78,0:09:58.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不会悲观
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.50,0:10:01.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在 有些人正在用与我们
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.14,0:10:05.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以及天行者所不同方法行动着
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.17,0:10:09.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这首歌是…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.02,0:10:13.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的 玛丽娜公主的歌正在向外传播
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.64,0:10:16.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,玛丽娜的歌在世界上…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.77,0:10:17.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.07,0:10:20.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想人们总是渴望和平的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.40,0:10:24.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,玛丽娜公主的歌描述了没有纷争
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.51,0:10:27.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,共同生存的世界
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.01,0:10:31.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也许我们只是在一味地否定他人
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.85,0:10:37.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而遗忘了相互理解的道理
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.68,0:10:41.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,相互理解…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.33,0:10:46.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,玛丽娜却一直在追求?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.26,0:10:48.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,相信这条道路的未来…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.65,0:10:58.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没有人出现在指定地点
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.58,0:11:03.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大小姐 天行者真的会来吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.56,0:11:06.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.04,0:11:10.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 不来的话 世界就会变为变革者所有
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.70,0:11:13.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,成为里本斯·阿尔马克的东西
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.00,0:11:16.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,尼娜·崔尼蒂什么时候站到变革者一边的?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.73,0:11:19.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别总是向别人提问 自己思考
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.72,0:11:21.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是因为你一直这样
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.04,0:11:23.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,才会让我成为王家的当家的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.22,0:11:27.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为哥哥你没有当家的气质
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.13,0:11:30.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的人生才扭曲了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.71,0:11:34.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以我才渴望世界的变革
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.88,0:11:37.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算是用地位、名誉和资产来交换
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.31,0:11:42.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的 我是为了修正自己的人生
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.65,0:11:44.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把握自己的将来
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.38,0:11:48.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,追随我到最后吧 红龙
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.29,0:11:52.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你有这个责任
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.33,0:11:57.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是什么腻歪的理由
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.21,0:11:59.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,无聊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.85,0:12:01.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你果然是笨蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.98,0:12:03.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,尼娜·崔尼蒂
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.80,0:12:05.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我最讨厌你了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.99,0:12:09.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,永别了 大小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.38,0:12:11.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,留美!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.06,0:12:19.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我最讨厌你了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.22,0:12:23.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,永别了 大小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.75,0:12:24.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,留美!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.59,0:12:33.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,红龙…!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.21,0:12:35.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,给我让开!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.86,0:12:39.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,兄长…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.21,0:12:41.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,留… 留美
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.93,0:12:45.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,活下去
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.68,0:12:46.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,兄长!!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.40,0:12:48.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这里由我…!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.73,0:12:50.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,碍事
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.51,0:12:56.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还耍帅
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.26,0:12:59.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,结束了么 结束了么
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.63,0:13:00.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在就先这样
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.71,0:13:02.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.82,0:13:03.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.83,0:13:06.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样计划就重写了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.22,0:13:09.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,既不是伊奥利亚也不是里本斯
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.78,0:13:11.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而是我自己的计划
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.06,0:13:16.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来了么
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.66,0:13:20.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,MS无法到达指定坐标
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.34,0:13:23.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,机体控制 交给你了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.64,0:13:24.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明白了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.46,0:13:34.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在前面么…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.80,0:13:53.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,刹那·F·塞艾
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.15,0:13:54.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,王留美?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.26,0:13:56.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了 受伤了么?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.32,0:14:01.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没有任何事情 不说了先拿着这个
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.50,0:14:03.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是什么
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.40,0:14:06.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,维塔本体的位置记录在上面
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.96,0:14:08.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,维塔本体么?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.87,0:14:10.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是被变革者得知这件事的话
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.20,0:14:12.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,维塔就会被转移
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.60,0:14:16.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一定要尽快 去夺回维塔
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.69,0:14:17.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明白了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.28,0:14:19.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一起从这里撤离吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.89,0:14:21.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我没关系的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.40,0:14:21.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.67,0:14:25.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是不能和你一起走的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.62,0:14:27.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要担心我了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.63,0:14:29.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.40,0:14:39.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我才不能和你们一起走的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.21,0:14:42.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为追求的东西可是不同的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.52,0:14:46.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,刹那!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.03,0:14:47.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.82,0:14:49.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊… 什么?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.46,0:14:51.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那架机体是…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.25,0:14:58.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,4年不见了啊 少年
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.01,0:14:59.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个男的是…!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.80,0:15:05.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你这混账…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.54,0:15:07.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,少年
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.78,0:15:09.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不想失去Gundam的话
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.68,0:15:11.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,希望你能够回应我的期望
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.73,0:15:13.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么期望?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.49,0:15:15.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,认真地决一胜负
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.46,0:15:17.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么!?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.46,0:15:21.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我 古拉哈姆·艾卡 但求与你做个了解
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.65,0:15:24.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Mr. 武士道…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.65,0:15:26.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是里本斯唆使他来的么
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.73,0:15:30.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不惜如此地想要决战么
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.33,0:15:32.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,当然
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.49,0:15:35.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在我的天空划下伤痕 将我的同胞和恩师夺去
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.49,0:15:37.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,连我作为Flag Fighter
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.56,0:15:40.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最后的尊严也尽数打碎的不是别人
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.47,0:15:41.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正是你和Gundam!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.31,0:15:43.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.83,0:15:47.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是已经超越了爱 又超越了憎恨
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.99,0:15:49.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,成为了我此生的宿命!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.74,0:15:50.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,宿命?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.61,0:15:53.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要笑我自作多情么
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.23,0:15:58.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 不要忘记了最初进行武力介入的可是Gundam!!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.45,0:16:00.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个男人也是…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.39,0:16:04.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为我们而歪曲了的存在…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.30,0:16:08.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明白了 我就接受在此了结吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.15,0:16:10.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,望你能尽全力
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.70,0:16:13.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沙慈 把控制交回这边来
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.61,0:16:14.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你准备跟他打?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.79,0:16:15.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没有其他的办法
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.86,0:16:22.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这就是我所期望的道路
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.80,0:16:25.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,修罗之路!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.19,0:16:29.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,00 Riser!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.56,0:16:31.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,豪杰加强版!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.75,0:16:32.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,将目标…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.53,0:16:34.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来吧 决一…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.56,0:16:35.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,驱逐!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.47,0:16:36.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,生死!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.22,0:16:43.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,天行者也好 变革者也好
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.72,0:16:48.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还有兄长献上性命 完成变革
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.01,0:16:52.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我会将那之后美好的未来…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.02,0:16:55.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那种东西 没可能会有吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.10,0:16:57.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,尼娜 为什么!?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.79,0:17:01.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说过的吧 我最讨厌的就是你
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.47,0:17:03.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,服从你只是为了活下去
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.32,0:17:07.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,稍微装得听话点你相信得还真快
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.48,0:17:09.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.08,0:17:12.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的使命已经结束了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.11,0:17:23.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,化成灰尘了呢～
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.19,0:17:27.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这就是你一直把人家当道具对待的惩罚
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.84,0:17:30.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我为了活下去的话什么都会去做
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.75,0:17:33.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为了得到幸福的话
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.69,0:17:37.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对的 服从变革者也是为了这个
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.93,0:17:40.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为哥哥们的仇都还没报
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.11,0:17:43.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,时机到了的话
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.65,0:17:46.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就让我隆重地反咬破你们的喉咙吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.78,0:17:48.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样的话你的使命也结束了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.44,0:17:50.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哈罗?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.35,0:17:52.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,乱来的家伙得要接受惩罚
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.97,0:17:54.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,变革者!?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.98,0:17:59.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对你的制裁者会出现的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.92,0:18:01.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说什么制裁者?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.57,0:18:02.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊…!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.39,0:18:06.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难道是 那家伙…?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.39,0:18:10.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有趣 哥哥们的仇人
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.75,0:18:13.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是呢 某种意义上说的确实算是仇人
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.55,0:18:17.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什 什么!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.06,0:18:19.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是它
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.53,0:18:22.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是那架Gundam!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.58,0:18:27.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把妈妈… 和爸爸杀掉的…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.72,0:18:29.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那时候的Gundam!!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.87,0:18:33.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么!?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.72,0:18:37.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那部机体 是Throne!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.34,0:18:39.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把露易丝家人杀掉的…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.83,0:18:41.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,住手 露易丝·哈勒维!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.62,0:18:42.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,露易丝?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.56,0:18:43.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那种复仇…!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.94,0:18:44.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,露易丝!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.12,0:18:46.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我说过要全力作战!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.36,0:18:54.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爸爸的仇人? 就算是我好了!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.51,0:18:57.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别以为就你张狂!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.83,0:19:09.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我被制造出来 被丢上战场…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.19,0:19:13.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么能死在 这种地方!!!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.58,0:19:18.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是呢 不想死吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.06,0:19:22.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 妈妈和爸爸…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.58,0:19:26.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,连这句话都没机会说!!!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.81,0:19:32.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可恶~~!!!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.48,0:19:37.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把Throne给…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.71,0:19:38.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,露易丝!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.73,0:19:40.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还不专心战斗吗!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.38,0:19:45.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Mr. 武士道正在和Gundam决斗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.61,0:19:47.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,准尉的机体呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.33,0:19:49.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在那里么
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.76,0:19:55.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,做到了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.12,0:19:58.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妈妈 爸爸
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.13,0:20:00.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我报仇了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.15,0:20:02.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我打倒Gundam了哦!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.04,0:20:04.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,准尉…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.80,0:20:13.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妈妈 爸爸 在哪里?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.50,0:20:15.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我做到了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.71,0:20:17.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,做到了哦…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.23,0:20:20.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,…所以……
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.64,0:20:22.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来夸奖我呀…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.91,0:20:27.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,…夸我…做得好吧……
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.85,0:22:17.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,活着的…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.57,0:22:20.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我就是为此活着的
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.37,0:22:24.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算要成为变革者的傀儡也好
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.66,0:22:27.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只有这武士道…!!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.02,0:22:31.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,做到这个地步…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.35,0:22:33.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,刹那!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.39,0:22:34.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,专心战斗
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.78,0:22:37.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样下去的话…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.97,0:22:40.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,根本了结不完
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.75,0:22:41.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.85,0:22:42.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,既然如此!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.08,0:22:44.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,TRANS-AM!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.14,0:22:47.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,TRANS-AM!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:05.37,0:23:07.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,终于 觉醒了么
Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.48,0:23:15.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这里究竟是…
Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.54,0:23:20.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是说我已经成佛涅磐了么
Dialogue: 0,0:23:21.09,0:23:21.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,错了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:24.44,0:23:25.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,少年?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.56,0:23:29.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这里是 量子集中的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.90,0:23:31.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在说什么梦话
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.92,0:23:33.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我觉得我明白了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.48,0:23:36.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,伊奥利亚·肖汉博格制造Gundam…
Dialogue: 0,0:23:37.40,0:23:40.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 制造GN-DRIVER的理由…
Dialogue: 0,0:23:41.22,0:23:41.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:42.91,0:23:45.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,武力介入只是为此的布局
Dialogue: 0,0:23:46.42,0:23:47.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,伊奥利亚的目的是
Dialogue: 0,0:23:48.24,0:23:50.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,引导人类的革新
Dialogue: 0,0:23:51.43,0:23:53.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的 我…
Dialogue: 0,0:23:54.65,0:23:56.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正在变革之中
Dialogue: 0,0:23:59.79,0:24:01.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为夺回维塔
Dialogue: 0,0:24:01.35,0:24:04.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,强行突破A-LAWS舰队的任务开始了
Dialogue: 0,0:24:05.46,0:24:06.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下集
Dialogue: 0,0:24:06.43,0:24:07.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为了未来
Dialogue: 0,0:24:08.50,0:24:09.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算要背负罪孽
Dialogue: 0,0:24:09.94,0:24:12.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要这战斗能另明日重生…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.30,0:00:01.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.10,0:10:18.83,IN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\a6\fs45}明日もいいことが　たくさんあるように
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.28,0:10:24.66,IN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\a6\fs45}お日様出て　夕陽きれいね
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.76,0:10:30.19,IN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\a6\fs45}星にねがい　明日が来る
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.35,0:10:35.38,IN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\a6\fs45}どうして行っちゃうの
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.03,0:10:41.15,IN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\a6\fs45}一緒に帰ろう
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.10,0:10:18.83,INcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\a6\fs36}明日也一定会称心如意
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.28,0:10:24.66,INcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\a6\fs36}阳光描绘的夕阳唯美如画
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.76,0:10:30.19,INcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\a6\fs36}向星辰祈愿明日的幸福
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.35,0:10:35.38,INcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\a6\fs36}为何要离开
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.03,0:10:41.15,INcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\a6\fs36}一起回家吧





